{"id":"5505","name":"happy-hour-across-the-sky","title":"Happy Hour: Across The Sky","author":"Christy Frink","date":"2010-08-05T18:30:00-05:00","tags":["basil marceaux","centennial park","dog park","election day","mnpd","NES","power outages","rocketown","severe weather"],"categories":["News"],"contentEncoded":"<div id=\"greet_block\"><noscript><div class=\"greet_block wpgb_cornered\"><div class=\"greet_text\"><div class=\"greet_image\"><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/feed/rss/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"http://nashvillest.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-greet-box/images/rss_icon.png\" alt=\"WP Greet Box icon\"></a></div>Hello there! If you&apos;re new to Nashvillest, you might want to <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/nashvillest\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>subscribe to our RSS feed</strong></a> to make sure you don&apos;t miss anything! We&apos;re also on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/nashvillest\" target=\"blank\"><strong>Twitter</strong></a> if you&apos;d like to join us there!<div style=\"clear:both\"></div><div class=\"greet_block_powered_by\">Powered by <a href=\"http://omninoggin.com/projects/wordpress-plugins/wp-greet-box-wordpress-plugin/\" title=\"WP Greet Box WordPress Plugin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">WP Greet Box</a> <a href=\"http://omninoggin.com/\" title=\"WordPress Plugin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">WordPress Plugin</a></div><div style=\"clear:both\"></div></div></div></noscript></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/drarkane/3637702730/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.flickr.com&apos;]);\"><img class=\"alignnone\" src=\"http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3309/3637702730_4d46a51424.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"334\"></a></div><ul><li>So about those storms! Lots of power outages all over Davidson County. A severe thunderstorm watch remains in effect until 8pm. [<a href=\"http://www.wkrn.com/global/story.asp?s=12932734\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wkrn.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">WKRN</a>]</li><li>On this fine Election Day&#x2013;otherwise known as the Most Convenient Day Of The Year For Every Tennessee State Government Website To Go Down&#x2013;every Tennessee state government website went down. Though it reportedly had nothing to do with the power outages, they were all down for several hours. [<a href=\"http://www.tennessean.com/article/20100805/NEWS02/100805049/-1/RSS05\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.tennessean.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Tennessean</a>]</li><li>Some local dog owners (206 at last count, according to the <a href=\"http://www.petitiononline.com/mod_perl/signed.cgi?focdp\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.petitiononline.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">petition</a>) are very upset because the Centennial Park renovations involve shrinking the dog parks and moving them closer together, meaning that smaller dogs could see and be intimidated by large dogs. [<a href=\"http://www.wsmv.com/news/24528202/detail.html\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wsmv.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">WSMV</a>]</li><li>Metro Police somehow accidentally misplaced 1,600 traffic stop videos, but claim that it was an outside contractor who deleted them. [<a href=\"http://www.tennessean.com/article/20100805/NEWS03/100805079/-1/RSS05\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.tennessean.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Tennessean</a>]</li><li>Congrats to Rocketown for their new digs, which opened today! [<a href=\"http://www.wkrn.com/global/story.asp?s=12933807\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wkrn.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">WKRN</a>]</li></ul><p><em>Photo by </em><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/drarkane/3637702730/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.flickr.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\"><em>drarkane</em></a><em>.</em></p><p>Related posts:<ol><li><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2010/04/27/happy-hour-whistling-in-the-dark-edition/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: Happy Hour: Whistling In The Dark Edition\">Happy Hour: Whistling In The Dark Edition</a></li></ol></p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<!--END .entry-content .article-->"}